SUMMARY:SOMMERKINO: „40 Years Of Fuckin´ Up“ (A film by NOFX) (Uhrzeit prüfen)
LOCATION:Arena
DESCRIPTION: | Arena Wien - Open Air | Einlass: 19:00 Filmbeginn: ca. 20:30 (bei Einbruch der Dunkelheit)  Dauer 125min Englische Original Fassung / Keine Untertitel  Ab 18 Jahren!  40 Years of Fuckin' Up is Spinal Tap\, but real. It's a film about the infamous\, fairly un-famous\, and beloved punk rock band NOFX. This is the unbelievable story about how a group of untalented drug-addled teenage punks somehow became the most successful independent band in history — and they did it haphazardly\, entirely on their own.  DIRECTOR James Buddy Day PRODUCER Fat Mike (Mike Burkett) DIRECTOR OF PHOTOGRAPHY Nathanial Harper SCORE Fat Mike & Matt Nasir PRODUCTION Pyramid Productions  Infos & Trailer: https://www.40yearsoffuckinup.com/  Vorverkauf Arena Shop € 15 (inkl. Fee)  Abendkassa tba. 
URL:https://arena.wien/Home/Programm-Detail/concert-id/48609
